item.title: How to make hair grow FASTER
item.description:
How to make hair grow FASTER
One of the most frequently asked questions I get regarding hair is 'Bubz, how can I make my hair grow faster?'. Now I'm no hair expert lol but I have learnt some handy tips here and there that you guys might find helpful. Your genetics play a MASSIVE role. Everybody's hair grows at different rates. Of course- your lifestyle and enviroment also plays a contribution. Remember there is no 'SOLID' method out there. However, there are ways you can prevent hair breakage, damage etc. Now this video isn't just going to cover methods to stimulate hair growth- but also how to maintain healthy hair. Why? First step to growing long hair is being able to maintain healthy hair. So I'll be covering ways to prevent hair loss & damage. Honestly- I am very low maintenance with my hair. My hair isn't exactly super healthy to be honest. Why? Because my hair is coloured. Pollution damages it. But I can only limit it's damage and try to pamper it as often as I can. I hope this video is helpful for you guys. I have to say- I am actually really liking my shorter hair. Make the most out of it =) Hair grows and this is even without you trying. Oh- I apologise about the shakiness. My cam was still set on 'Face detection' so when I move- it moves too. I'm a camera noob. I filmed this same day as I filmed the Japan Haul so these two videos were shakey. *face palm* I normally don't really recommend taking hair growth supplements but it's entirely up to you. Talk to a doctor/expert before trusting 'pills'. Even if its '100% natural'. I trust you guys to be able to know what is good for your body and not. item.title: Ductos de PEMEX explotan en San Martin Texmelucan
item.description:
Ductos de PEMEX explotan en San Martin Texmelucan
Ductos de PEMEX explotan en San Martin Texmelucan, ductos de PEMEX explotan en San Martin Texmelucan, Habitantes del Municipio San Martín Texmelucan son desalojados de sus viviendas a consecuencia de una explosión de un ducto de Petróleos Mexicanos (Pemex). Entre las principales colonias afectadas están El Arenal, Solidaridad, El Cerrito, así como las zonas aledañas al tianguis de San Martín Texmelucan. Hasta el momento no existe un reporte oficial, sin embargo, elementos del Heroico Cuerpo de Bomberos informaron que alrededor de las 5:00 horas se registró la primera explosión y que hay al menos un muerto. Se presume que el combustible se regó en las aguas del río Atoyac, canal que hasta el momento arde en llamas. La gente que aún permanece en el lugar intenta frenar el avance del fuego con cubetas y extintores, particularmente en el área cercana a las bodegas del tianguis, donde ya se han registrado explosiones de tanques de gas. se habla de 11 calcinados, 12 heridos, y 32 casas afectadas
